You can configure your Slack bot to do this:

...just by writing this code:

bot.calculations = { countUsers: { question: 'How many users were active {in date range}?', type: 'count', state: { count: 0 }, aggregator: (state, visits) => { if(visits.length > 0){ state.count++; } return state; }, response: (state) => { return `I counted ${state.count} users.`; } } ... }
